sec.p:
Four plasmids containing different shRNA directed against human TRPM8 and a plasmid containing non-targeting shRNA were obtained from Superarray Biosciences/Qiagen (Valencia, CA, USA) and tested for efficiency of gene silencing. An shRNA under control of U1 promoter and green fluorescent protein (GFP) reporter gene are contained in each plasmid. The sequences of the anti-TRPM8 shRNA were:


5'-AAACTTAGGACCCAAGATTAT-3'; 5'-AAGGAACTCTCCAAAGTCATT-3';

5'-AAACACCCAACCTGGTCATTT-3'; 5'-CAACGACACCTCAGAGGAAAT-3'.
